---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="App Privacy Policy - RoyalPromptss" description="Simple privacy policy for RoyalPromptss mobile app - Anonymous usage with minimal data collection.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">RoyalPromptss App Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        <strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024
      </p>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
              <strong>Privacy First:</strong> RoyalPrompts uses anonymous login only. We don't collect personal information like names, emails, or phone numbers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What We Collect</h2>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Anonymous Device Information</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Anonymous device identifier (no personal info linked)</li>
        <li>App version and device type (Android/iOS)</li>
        <li>Basic usage statistics (features used, app crashes)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">What We DON'T Collect</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>❌ Names, emails, or phone numbers</li>
        <li>❌ Location data</li>
        <li>❌ Personal photos or files</li>
        <li>❌ Contact lists or messages</li>
        <li>❌ Browsing history</li>
        <li>❌ Social media accounts</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We only use anonymous data to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Make the app work properly</li>
        <li>Fix bugs and improve performance</li>
        <li>Understand which features are most popular</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Anonymous Login</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        RoyalPrompts uses anonymous login, which means:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>No account creation required</li>
        <li>No email or password needed</li>
        <li>Your data is linked only to your device</li>
        <li>You can use the app immediately after download</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Your app data (favorites, created prompts) is stored:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Locally on your device</li>
        <li>Anonymously on our servers (no personal info attached)</li>
        <li>Securely encrypted</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may use these services for app functionality:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Google Play Services:</strong> For app distribution and updates</li>
        <li><strong>App Store:</strong> For iOS app distribution</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous usage statistics only</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Our app is safe for all ages. We don't collect personal information from anyone, including children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Since we don't collect personal information, you can:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Delete the app anytime (removes all local data)</li>
        <li>Clear app data in your device settings</li>
        <li>Contact us if you have questions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Questions about privacy? Contact us at:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@royalprompts.online<br>
          <strong>Response:</strong> Within 48 hours
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may update this policy occasionally. We'll notify users through app updates.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mt-8">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
              <strong>Simple Summary:</strong> RoyalPrompts is designed with privacy in mind. We use anonymous login and collect minimal data to provide you with the best AI prompt experience without compromising your privacy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
